    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/2049c6f5389b8e7d6f33bbc1fc8b1bc6.poster.avif?t=1750356193\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/2049c6f5389b8e7d6f33bbc1fc8b1bc6.webm?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/2049c6f5389b8e7d6f33bbc1fc8b1bc6.mp4?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>漫威：超级争霸战现已登陆 Steam</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >终极漫威争霸战现已登陆 PC！进入战场，体验史诗般的 1 对 1 战斗，与漫威宇宙中你最喜欢的超级英雄和恶人一决高下——现在已全面优化，可在大屏幕上使用鼠标、键盘和控制器进行操作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/4db74021897f05b97f878337019e30f0.poster.avif?t=1750356193\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/4db74021897f05b97f878337019e30f0.webm?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/4db74021897f05b97f878337019e30f0.mp4?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组建你的漫威梦之队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为收藏家选中的召唤者，从 300 多名英雄中组建一支强大的团队，包括标志性的复仇者联盟、X 战警、银河护卫队、蜘蛛侠英雄等！无论你是将钢铁侠与金刚狼组队，还是让死侍与毒液对决，组合无穷无尽，赌注也越来越高。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/d36be49b362362d5b4400924bb96508c.poster.avif?t=1750356193\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/d36be49b362362d5b4400924bb96508c.webm?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/d36be49b362362d5b4400924bb96508c.mp4?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗赢得胜利</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与来自世界各地的敌人与玩家展开快节奏的战斗。掌握直观的战斗机制，在电影般的剧情、竞技场和限时活动中释放必杀技。每场战斗都让你离成为战场冠军更近一步！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/26c2192bde8b72b23b16cd09de62ff8e.poster.avif?t=1750356193\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/26c2192bde8b72b23b16cd09de62ff8e.webm?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/26c2192bde8b72b23b16cd09de62ff8e.mp4?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>史诗任务，经典故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在惊险刺激的 Marvel 风格故事中，探索不断发展的剧情。在战场上完成任务，探索新章节，面对强大的头目，揭开多宇宙的谜团。每次更新都会带来新鲜内容和新的英雄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/e9f9c9f1ae3bdb6e2c97dff543d25c38.poster.avif?t=1750356193\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/e9f9c9f1ae3bdb6e2c97dff543d25c38.webm?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/e9f9c9f1ae3bdb6e2c97dff543d25c38.mp4?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组队，登顶</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他召唤者组队，组建强大的联盟。协调策略，参加全球活动，统治联盟战争和联盟任务，赢得珍贵奖励，攀登竞技排名。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/cc12a1e93174480bd81b21da05518117.poster.avif?t=1750356193\" width=600 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/cc12a1e93174480bd81b21da05518117.webm?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127280/extras/cc12a1e93174480bd81b21da05518117.mp4?t=1750356193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>随时随地玩</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《漫威：超级争霸战》已针对 Steam 重新打造，原生支持控制器、键盘和鼠标，并可自定义绑定。享受全面的跨平台支持——在移动设备上开始旅程，然后在 PC 上无缝继续。无论您在何处玩，您的进度都会随您而行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>争霸战在等待</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫威宇宙的命运掌握在您手中。您会迎接挑战，带领您的冠军取得胜利吗？</p>",
